snippet.title: Ninja Chop!! | Xbox 360
snippet.description:
Hey, does anyone remember the Xbox Live Indie Games? Well, actually I don't know if I really want to remember them, but "Ninja Chop!!" is just crazy. :0
SUBSCRIBE ► http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7wkTM_h3HsXb1EsVK6Imbw?sub_confirmation=1 
AND FOLLOW ME DOWN THE RABBIT HOLE!

Note: "Milk! More Milk! Mooooo!"
